FLEMINGTON COAL & COKE CO. v. WELLS. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 6, 1903.) No. 102. In Error to the Circuit Court of the United States for the Eastern District of New York. Eldon Bisbee, for plaintiff in error. Herbert Green, for defendant in error.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

No opinion. Judgment of Circuit Court affirmed.
